Processes and Resources Manager



file:
- makefile
- manager.h
- manager.c
- shell.c
- shell.h
- readme

the structure of process control block.



the structure of resource control block.



the operations of process.
- create
- destroy
- suspend*
- activate*


the operations of resource.
- request
- release


the structure of shell and manager.


commands of presentation shell:
- init                              // initilize manager
- cr <process name> <priority>      // create process 
- de <process name>                 // delete process
- req <resource> <# of units>       // request resource
- rel <resource name> <# of units>  // release resource
- to                                // time-out interrupt
- list ready                        // list all process in ready list
- list block                        // list all process in blocked list
- list res                          // list all available resources
- pr <process name>*                // print pcb information about a given process

ps:
# indicate that the argument is optional.
* indicate that the command is optional.


